    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "title: \"Valutazione delle Performance di una MLP nella Classificazione del Dataset Wine\"\n",
        "format:\n",
        "  html:\n",
        "    theme: pulse\n",
        "    css: style.css\n",
        "    self-contained: true # Se Quarto ti dà ancora errore qui, cambialo in: embed-resources: true\n",
        "    toc: true\n",
        "    toc-depth: 3\n",
        "    toc-title: \"Indice\"\n",
        "    title-block-banner: images/banner2.png\n",
        "    mermaid:\n",
        "      theme: default\n",
        "    other-links:\n",
        "      - text: AI4I 2020 Predictive Maintenance Dataset\n",
        "        href: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/dataset/601/ai4i+2020+predictive+maintenance+dataset\n",
        "    code-links:\n",
        "      - text: Codice sorgente\n",
        "        icon: file-code\n",
        "        href: ReportQuartoHTML.qmd\n",
        "\n",
        "editor: visual\n",
        "jupyter: python3\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "```{=html}\n",
        "<script>\n",
        "document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", () => {\n",
        "  const banner = document.querySelector(\".quarto-title-block .quarto-title-banner\");\n",
        "  const title  = document.querySelector(\".quarto-title-block .title\");\n",
        "  if (!banner || !title) return;\n",
        "  \n",
        "  const H_MAX = 240;\n",
        "  const H_MIN = 56;\n",
        "  const RANGE = 260;\n",
        "  \n",
        "  banner.style.height = H_MAX + \"px\";\n",
        "  \n",
        "  let lastKnownScrollY = 0;\n",
        "  let ticking = false;\n",
        "  let lastHeight = H_MAX;\n",
        "  \n",
        "  function update() {\n",
        "    const s = Math.min(lastKnownScrollY, RANGE);\n",
        "    const t = s / RANGE;\n",
        "    const h = H_MAX - (H_MAX - H_MIN) * t;\n",
        "    \n",
        "    const roundedH = Math.round(h * 2) / 2;\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if (Math.abs(roundedH - lastHeight) >= 0.5) {\n",
        "      lastHeight = roundedH;\n",
        "      banner.style.height = roundedH + \"px\";\n",
        "      \n",
        "      if (roundedH <= H_MIN + 2) {\n",
        "        banner.classList.add(\"is-collapsed\");\n",
        "      } else {\n",
        "        banner.classList.remove(\"is-collapsed\");\n",
        "      }\n",
        "    }\n",
        "    \n",
        "    ticking = false;\n",
        "  }\n",
        "  \n",
        "  function onScroll(){\n",
        "    lastKnownScrollY = window.scrollY;\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if (!ticking) {\n",
        "      window.requestAnimationFrame(update);\n",
        "      ticking = true;\n",
        "    }\n",
        "  }\n",
        "  \n",
        "  window.addEventListener(\"scroll\", onScroll, { passive: true });\n",
        "  onScroll();\n",
        "});\n",
        "</script>\n",
        "```"
      ],
      "id": "4d46eb8c"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#|echo: false\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from sklearn.datasets import load_wine\n",
        "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
        "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
        "from sklearn.neural_network import MLPClassifier\n",
        "from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix"
      ],
      "id": "7b699bdd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Il Dataset si compone di 178 osservazioni campionarie.\n",
        "\n",
        "Carichiamo il dataset <code>Wine</code> presente all'interno del pacchetto <code>scikit-learn</code>."
      ],
      "id": "1cdc1e15"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "wine = load_wine()"
      ],
      "id": "4c41b3f8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Adesso procediamo ad estrarre le Feature ed il Target"
      ],
      "id": "cadec15b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "X = wine.data\n",
        "y = wine.target"
      ],
      "id": "24966b3a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Data cleaning\n",
        "\n",
        "Creiamo un <b>DataFrame</b> associando ad ogni colonna il nome della rispettiva variabile. Aggiungiamo inoltre una colonna che per convenzione chiameremo <code>Target</code>."
      ],
      "id": "590a4b8b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "df = pd.DataFrame(X, columns=wine.feature_names)\n",
        "df[\"Target\"] = y"
      ],
      "id": "6cff37b0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Andiamo a <b>rinominare</b> le variabili del dataframe così da rendere gli output più intellegibili:"
      ],
      "id": "372a538a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "rename_var = {\n",
        "    \"alcohol\": \"Alcol\",\n",
        "    \"malic_acid\": \"Acido Malico\",\n",
        "    \"ash\": \"Ceneri\",\n",
        "    \"alcalinity_of_ash\": \"Alcalinità delle Ceneri\",\n",
        "    \"magnesium\": \"Magnesio\",\n",
        "    \"total_phenols\": \"Fenoli Totali\",\n",
        "    \"flavanoids\": \"Flavonoidi\",\n",
        "    \"nonflavanoid_phenols\": \"Fenoli Non Flavonoidi\",\n",
        "    \"proanthocyanins\": \"Proantocianidine\",\n",
        "    \"color_intensity\": \"Intensità Colore\",\n",
        "    \"hue\": \"Tonalità\",\n",
        "    \"od280/od315_of_diluted_wines\": \"Densità Ottica (OD Ratio)\",\n",
        "    \"proline\": \"Prolina\",\n",
        "    \"Target\": \"Vigneto\"\n",
        "}"
      ],
      "id": "c26b52f2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#|echo: false\n",
        "df_clean = df.rename(columns=rename_var)"
      ],
      "id": "661cca3e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Stampiamo le prime 10 osservazioni del nostro set di dati:"
      ],
      "id": "d3d03b44"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#|echo: false\n",
        "\n",
        "# 3. Prendi le prime 10 righe e trasponi\n",
        "df_verticale = df_clean.head(10).T\n",
        "\n",
        "# --- LA MODIFICA QUI ---\n",
        "# Rinominiamo le colonne da 0..9 a \"1^ unità\"..\"10^ unità\"\n",
        "df_verticale.columns = [f\"unità {i+1}\" for i in range(len(df_verticale.columns))]\n",
        "# -----------------------\n",
        "\n",
        "posizione_penultima = df_verticale.index.get_loc(df_verticale.index[-2])\n",
        "\n",
        "df_stilizzato = (df_verticale.style\n",
        "    # 1. Formattazione dei numeri\n",
        "    .format(lambda x: f\"{x:g}\" if isinstance(x, (float, int)) else x)\n",
        "    \n",
        "    # 2. Inserimento della linea nera continua sotto l'intera riga (incluso l'indice)\n",
        "    .set_table_styles([\n",
        "        {\n",
        "            # Seleziona l'ennesima riga del corpo della tabella (i fogli di stile partono da 1, quindi +1)\n",
        "            'selector': f'tbody tr:nth-child({posizione_penultima + 1})',\n",
        "            'props': [('border-bottom', '1px solid black')]\n",
        "        }\n",
        "    ])\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "df_stilizzato"
      ],
      "id": "e829932b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Variabili feature\n",
        "\n",
        "### Struttura e proprietà Chimico-Fisiche\n",
        "Variabili che descrivono la composizione generale del vino.\n",
        "\n",
        "```{=html}\n",
        "<div class=\"feature-card\">\n",
        "\n",
        "  <div class=\"feature-card-header\">\n",
        "    <h3 id=\"air-temperature\">Alcohol</h3>\n",
        "\n",
        "    <div class=\"feature-card-labels\">\n",
        "      <span class=\"feature-label label-type\">Variabile quantitativa continua</span>\n",
        "      <span class=\"feature-label label-unit\">% vol</span>\n",
        "\n",
        "    </div>\n",
        "\n",
        "  </div>\n",
        "\n",
        "  <div class=\"feature-card-body\">\n",
        "    <div class=\"feature-card-grid\">\n",
        "\n",
        "      <div class=\"feature-card-plot\">\n",
        "```"
      ],
      "id": "4ffcc2e5"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| echo: false\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
